File Types:
1:main.tf – main configuration
2:Variables.tf – define variables
3:terraform.tfvars – input values
4:outputs.tf – outputs of execution

Command	Purpose
terraform init	Initializes the working dir
terraform plan	Shows what will be created
terraform apply	Applies the changes
terraform destroy	Destroys the resources
terraform fmt	Formats code
terraform validate	Checks for syntax issues
terraform init        # Initializes Terraform
terraform plan        # Shows what will be created
terraform apply       # Applies the plan and creates resources
